reviewText: I bought this along with several others and I always reach for it every time I want to play his material.  I had never seen Daniel and Majella so candid and loving.  I am so glad I have this one and I would say everybody should have it to enjoy.  Inez
Bought this for my mom.  It would not play on any dvd player. Sent it back and received same dvd meant for europe,obviously! They should have specified this.
